Review.create(rating: 5.0, first_name: "Jim", last_initial: "O.", location: "Amherst, NH", description: "I hired this company to hide the speaker wires for the surround sound. The install looks fantastic! The job turned out to be tougher than expected, but Tim promptly returned to finish the job. He also helped me by providing a \"tour\" of the system and uncovered features that I did not know I had -- this guy knows his stuff. A very helpful, courteous and professional outfit.")
